0008#STR0008#ALL#Selecting Files. . .
0009#STR0009#ALL#Enter the initial instrument of the selection range. 
0010#STR0010#ALL#Enter the final instrument of the selection range or fill in the field with Çz` to select all of them. 
0011#STR0011#ALL#Enter the initial date related to the instruments selection period.
0012#STR0012#ALL#Enter the final date related to the instruments selection period
0013#STR0013#ALL#Enter the initial department of the selection interval or let the field empty to select all of them.
0014#STR0014#ALL#Enter the final department of the selection interval or fill in the whole field with the letter Çz` to select all of them.
0015#STR0015#ALL#Select the desired calibrating body: Only the calibrations carried out internally, externally or both.
0016#STR0016#ALL#If you choice was internal calibrating body or both, enter the initial calibrating body or let the field empty to select all of them.
0017#STR0017#ALL#If you choice was internal calibrating body or both, enter the final calibrating body or fill in the whole field with the letter Çz` to select all of them.
0018#STR0018#ALL#If you choice was external calibrating body or both, enter the initial calibrating body or let the field empty to select all of them.
0019#STR0019#ALL#If you choice was external calibrating body or both, enter the final calibrating body or fill in the whole field with the letter Çz` to select all of them.
0020#STR0020#ALL#Enter the initial family of the selection interval or let it empty to select all of them.
0021#STR0021#ALL#Enter the final family of the selection interval or fill in the whole field with the letter Çz` to select all of them.
0022#STR0022#ALL#Enter the initial user of the selection interval or let it empty to select all of them.
0023#STR0023#ALL#Enter the final user of the selection interval or fill in the whole field with the letter Çz` to select all of them.
0024#STR0024#ALL#Enter the initial manufacturer of the selection interval or let it empty to select all of them.
